tasks have been assigned

00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:21.540
to some individual person.

00:03:21.540 --> 00:03:24.260
Maybe you've got something
like all your priority

00:03:24.260 --> 00:03:26.720
one stuff done.

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:27.554
All that is cleared.

00:03:27.554 --> 00:03:29.178
All the most important
things got done.

00:03:29.178 --> 00:03:29.679
We are fine.

00:03:29.679 --> 00:03:32.219
