is capable of
finishing their task.

00:04:03.730 --> 00:04:07.170
So if you've got like a
giant list of priorities--

00:04:07.170 --> 00:04:09.580
if I were to take this list
of priority one, priority

00:04:09.580 --> 00:04:12.950
two, priority three and
forced sat you down and went

00:04:12.950 --> 00:04:15.380
through the arduous
process of actually giving

00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:18.608
each individual task a
separate priority number

00:04:18.608 --> 00:04:20.649
so that you could actually
solve it and rank it--

00:04:20.649 --> 00:04:21.779
I'm going to do that.

00:04:21.779 --> 00:04:23.695
Because I know it takes
a heck of a long time.

00:04:23.695 --> 00:04:27.490
