00:05:10.090 --> 00:05:12.195
But, it is possible
that in your head,

00:05:12.195 --> 00:05:14.070
you actually have that
level of granularity--

00:05:14.070 --> 00:05:17.500
that you actually know in
your team what that highest

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:20.382
level undone task is,
even though they all

00:05:20.382 --> 00:05:21.340
have the same priority.

00:05:21.340 --> 00:05:24.220
They're all priority two
tasks, or something like that.

00:05:24.220 --> 00:05:29.950
So something that will be useful
before you depart class today

00:05:29.950 --> 00:05:33.660
is to actually figure out--
off all of the things that

00:05:33.660 --> 00:05:35.820
are the highest
priority and undone

00:05:35.820 --> 00:05:39.740
right now, what is really
the most important thing?

00:05:39.740 --> 00:05:43.140
