00:05:43.140 --> 00:05:46.410
In fact, all of your
highest priority tasks

00:05:46.410 --> 00:05:48.670
should all be
assigned to somebody.

00:05:48.670 --> 00:05:52.770
And you should have a good
sense of what order of priority

00:05:52.770 --> 00:05:53.350
